  "privacySectionYourRights": "۴. حقوق شما",
  "privacyRightsBody": "You have the following rights regarding your data: • Access: View همه your personal and سلامت data within the app or request a data eخروجی • Correction: ویرایش your پروفایل information at any زمان through ویرایش Pپروفایل • Deletion: Request account deletion through تنظیمات > Data & حریم خصوصی > حذف Account. • Restriction: Limit how certain data is processed by adjusting your notification and sharing preferences. • Objection: Object to specific data processing activities by contacting our Data Protection Officer. • Withdrawal of Consent: You may withdraw consent at any زمان without affecting the lawfulness of prior processing. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at privacy@vitalseker.com or through the in-app پشتیبانی feature.",
